# David Cole ‚Äì Personal Portfolio Website

Welcome to my personal portfolio website! This project showcases my front-end web development skills using modern HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript. It is fully responsive, accessible, and designed to function as both a learning exercise and a professional showcase.

---

## üåê About This Project

This site was built to:
- Highlight my web development abilities  
- Demonstrate real-world use of HTML/CSS/JavaScript  
- Present personal content in an engaging, standards-compliant format  
- Serve as a public-facing example of my work for potential collaborators and employers

---

## üéØ Key Features

- **Responsive Layout:** Built using mobile-first design principles
- **Interactive Elements:** Email copy buttons, dynamic date rendering, and simple form scripting
- **Media Integration:** Includes custom video, audio, and images
- **CSS Visuals:** Animated starfield background using DOM and style manipulation
- **Print-Friendly:** Optimized layout for printing with clean formatting
- **Accessibility:** Uses semantic tags and logical navigation for screen readers

